{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 1,
      "name": "Home",
      "item": "https://yourdomain.com"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 2,
      "name": "[Category Name]",
      "item": "https://yourdomain.com/category"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 3,
      "name": "[Subcategory Name]",
      "item": "https://yourdomain.com/category/subcategory"
    },
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": 4,
      "name": "[Current Page Name]",
      "item": "https://yourdomain.com/category/subcategory/page"
    }
  ]
}

/*
USAGE NOTES:

1. Breadcrumb Benefits:
   - Shows site structure in search results
   - Improves navigation understanding
   - Displays in Google mobile results
   - Helps AI understand content hierarchy
   - Better user experience

2. Position:
   - Must start at 1 (Home page)
   - Sequential numbering (1, 2, 3, 4...)
   - No gaps in sequence
   - Minimum 2 items (Home + Current)

3. Item URLs:
   - Must be absolute URLs (https://...)
   - Each level should be accessible
   - Should match actual page URLs
   - Include trailing slashes consistently

4. Name:
   - Use actual page titles
   - Keep concise (2-5 words)
   - Match visible breadcrumb text
   - Use title case or sentence case consistently

5. Best Practices:
   - Include on every page except homepage
   - Maximum 5-7 levels deep
   - Skip unnecessary intermediate levels if very deep
   - Last item is current page
   - Match HTML breadcrumb navigation

HTML BREADCRUMB (Place in page):
<nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
  <ol>
    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="/category">Category</a></li>
    <li><a href="/category/subcategory">Subcategory</a></li>
    <li aria-current="page">Current Page</li>
  </ol>
</nav>

EXAMPLES:

E-commerce:
Home > Products > Skincare > Anti-Aging > Retinol Serum

Blog:
Home > Blog > Longevity > Biomarkers > LDL Cholesterol Guide

Service Site:
Home > Services > Consulting > Strategy > Market Entry

Medical:
Home > Treatments > Aesthetic > Botox > What to Expect

GOOGLE DISPLAY:
yourdomain.com › Category › Subcategory › Current Page

AI BENEFITS:

ChatGPT:
- Understands content hierarchy
- Places page in site context
- Better topic categorization

Perplexity:
- Shows related content paths
- Improves site navigation
- Better content discovery

Claude:
- Validates content organization
- Understands site structure
- Better context interpretation

Gemini:
- Integrates with site structure
- Displays in search results
- Mobile-friendly navigation

DYNAMIC GENERATION (Example - JavaScript):

function generateBreadcrumb(path) {
  const parts = path.split('/').filter(p => p);
  const items = [{
    "@type": "ListItem",
    "position": 1,
    "name": "Home",
    "item": "https://yourdomain.com"
  }];

  let currentPath = "https://yourdomain.com";
  parts.forEach((part, index) => {
    currentPath += `/${part}`;
    items.push({
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": index + 2,
      "name": formatName(part),
      "item": currentPath
    });
  });

  return {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": items
  };
}

PLACEMENT:
Add to every page (except homepage):
<script type="application/ld+json">
[PASTE JSON HERE]
</script>

TESTING:
- Google Rich Results Test: https://search.google.com/test/rich-results
- Verify all URLs are accessible
- Check mobile display
- Test with Google Search Console
*/
